    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1. 游戏简介 (Short Description)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“我发誓，一定让你上天堂！”</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在疲惫人生的尽头，天使艾莉尔（Ariel）带来的甜蜜提案。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >唯一的条件？就是通过志愿活动赚取“天堂点数”！与青梅竹马海媛、社会福利师娜妍，以及艾莉尔一起投身于这项乱来的计划。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你究竟能否平安抵达天堂？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2. 关于这款游戏 (About This Game)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252460/extras/06601ebd1d8ee2def7c8a966f8f41245.avif?t=1772470372\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252460/extras_big/06601ebd1d8ee2def7c8a966f8f41245.avif?t=1772470372 width=1560 height=890 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >📖 故事概要</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在充满疲惫的人生的终点，古灵精怪的天使<strong>“艾莉尔”</strong>出现在你面前，并带来了一个令人震惊的消息。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“喂，你想去天堂的话，分数好像还有点不够哦？”</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了拿到通往乐园的门票，时间所剩无几！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你必须留在人间，通过在流浪狗收容所、育幼院和养老院做义工来收集<strong>“天堂点数”</strong>。你并不孤单——值得信赖的青梅竹马<strong>“李海媛”</strong>和充满热情的社会福利师<strong>“金娜妍”</strong>会助你一臂之力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充满欢笑、泪水与温情的最后（也许是？）旅程，现在开始。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >📅 改变命运的日程管理</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在艾莉尔被召回天界之前，你必须达成目标！每一天都至关重要。通过打工赚钱，通过休息管理压力，并提升你的志愿服务能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252460/extras/13d8b91c4578f6bc57b31f3ed15475a1.avif?t=1772470372\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>成长系统：</strong> 通过活动获取经验值并升级。利用升级获得的“特质点数（Trait Points）”解锁技能，让日程管理和小游戏变得更加轻松。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多重结局：</strong> 你的选择和成就将决定你与女主角们的未来。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 3种独特的志愿活动小游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不仅仅是阅读文本！每个志愿服务场所都有独特玩法的游戏在等着你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🐶 流浪狗收容所（障碍闪避动作）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252460/extras/2dd0a2567b3476afab34f6dd9339831e.poster.avif?t=1772470372\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252460/extras/2dd0a2567b3476afab34f6dd9339831e.webm?t=1772470372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252460/extras/2dd0a2567b3476afab34f6dd9339831e.mp4?t=1772470372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带精力充沛的狗狗们去散步吧！ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要灵活躲避突然出现的障碍物，安全完成散步。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >中心负责人<strong>“和尚”</strong>会用慈悲之心为你加油！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🧸 育幼院（类幸存者射击）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252460/extras/345e62f1484f471e893e477d41e271f5.poster.avif?t=1772470372\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252460/extras/345e62f1484f471e893e477d41e271f5.webm?t=1772470372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252460/extras/345e62f1484f471e893e477d41e271f5.mp4?t=1772470372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和孩子们玩耍简直就是战场！ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用各种玩具武器击退成群结队的“僵尸（正在玩耍的孩子们）”。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的目标是与中心负责人<strong>“修女”</strong>一起耗尽他们的体力。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>👵 养老院（塔防）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252460/extras/ee251b731be92f20aa95a2f003075b14.poster.avif?t=1772470372\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252460/extras/ee251b731be92f20aa95a2f003075b14.webm?t=1772470372\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252460/extras/ee251b731be92f20aa95a2f003075b14.mp4?t=1772470372\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与老奶奶们一起进行的大扫除作战！ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >必须阻挡不断涌来的“灰尘”。将老奶奶们以此策略性地配置在关键位置，消灭灰尘。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别忘了中心负责人<strong>“牧师”</strong>的祝福！</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >❤️ 充满魅力的女主角与协力者</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252460/extras/f122f15b16ac3e6f190d9488a1912977.avif?t=1772470372\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252460/extras_big/f122f15b16ac3e6f190d9488a1912977.avif?t=1772470372 width=1560 height=890 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>阿丽埃尔 (Ariel)：</strong> 提出天堂点数交易的古灵精怪的天使。在她返回天空之前，你得跟她算清这笔账（？）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>李慧温 (Lee Hyewon)：</strong> 毫不犹豫挺身而出帮助你的可靠青梅竹马。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>金娜妍 (Kim Nayeon)：</strong> 一丝不苟且真诚的新人社会福利师。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以及实现了真正宗教大和谐（？）的收容所和尚、育幼院修女和养老院牧师。这些个性十足的协力者将支持你的天堂之旅。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✨ 游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252460/extras/99192e8ca4056b7457010410a1eaa239.avif?t=1772470372\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252460/extras_big/99192e8ca4056b7457010410a1eaa239.avif?t=1772470372 width=1560 height=890 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >融合了幽默与感动的扎实剧本。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以追求不同女主角的多重结局系统。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RPG式的特质系统，享受角色养成的乐趣。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含动作、类幸存者（Survivor-like）、塔防等3种不同类型的小游戏。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超越宗教界限的爆笑配角们。</p></li></ul>",
